      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s been absolutely pampered and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It drives like a dream and is in pristine shape inside and out. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and well-kept, this is the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
