      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a concours-level 2008 BMW M3 (E92) in Alpine White. This specimen features the S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, a masterpiece of high-revving engineering with an 8,400 RPM redline and eight individual throttle bodies. The rod bearings and throttle actuators\u2014critical preventative maintenance items\u2014have been professionally addressed with full documentation. The Carbon Fiber Reinforced Plastic (CFRP) roof is flawless, ensuring a low center of gravity and structural rigidity. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile, short-throw engagement, while the M Variable Differential Lock ensures surgical precision through corners. With original factory paint and a completely stock configuration, this is the definitive driver's car for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Clean title. No mechanical issues. Flawless interior and exterior. Garage kept.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
