      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exemplary specimen in showroom condition, a vehicle that has been treated more as a prized collection piece than a daily driver. The exterior finish is flawless, retaining its original deep factory luster with absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings. It has been kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen rain or snow. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery is firm and supple with zero bolster wear, and the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty mats since day one. Every switch, dial, and digital display operates with factory precision. Mechanically, this car is perfect. It features a full, documented service history with every oil change and inspection performed ahead of schedule by brand specialists. The undercarriage is as clean as the body, and the engine bay is detailed to a high standard. This sale includes the original window sticker, all owner\u2019s manuals, two sets of keys, and a custom-fitted car cover. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a 'like-new' example for the discerning enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 44500.0,
